{"id": "xgp1665702917460", "title": "Rollback ('R')", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "API Reference", "APIs: Database Connector Interface", "Database Connector Requests", "Rollback ('R')"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgp1665702917460.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Rollback ('R')</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: Open ('O')  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: Open ('O')  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rha1665702916756.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: Select ('S')\" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: Select ('S')\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kud1665702916962.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgp1665702917460.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgp1665702917460.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgp1665702917460.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533719\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533719\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xgp1665702917460.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgp1665702917460.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgp1665702917460.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xgp1665702917460\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Roll back the transaction.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__section_znh_3jx_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812759e50\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__p_d130493e1_d130494e1_d130495e1\">Roll back the transaction on the current logon path.\n        If the DBMS does not support Rollback, return 0 to Uniface.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__p_d130496e1_d130497e1_d130498e1\">Connectors that are TM-controlled\n          (<code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;TMEnabled</code> = 1) will not receive any Commit or Rollback\n        requests.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__section_gsp_rtx_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812759e65\">From Uniface</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Preconditions realized by Uniface—The connector is logged on to the DBMS.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Information Available from Uniface</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\">Data Structure-&gt;Element</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;iobuf</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Points to the general I/O buffer.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;sqlbuf</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Points to the SQL buffer.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;uchfw</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Uniface virtual address of the next control\n                block.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;uchbw</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Uniface virtual address of the previous control\n                block.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvini</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Unique identification of the current logon\n                path.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvnum</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Connector sequence number.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;ulock</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15596e1_d15597e1_d15598e1__entry__2\">Lock indicator.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__section_pjg_stx_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812759e180\">To Uniface</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">Rollback</code> request is provided with a dummy control block. This control\n        block does not describe a table and it does not have an associated connector workspace.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__p_d130511e1_d130512e1_d130513e1\">If the connector maintains the field\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;ulock</code> and the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Rollback</code> has succeeded,\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;ulock</code> must be set to 0 for every control block that meets all\n        the following criteria:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__ul_kdn_wtx_bcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__li_d46802e1_d46803e1_d46804e1\">It is for the DBMS driven by this connector\n            (<code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvnum</code> equals <code class=\"ph codeph\">udrvnum</code> in the first control\n          block).</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__li_d46805e1_d46806e1_d46807e1\">It belongs to the current logon path\n            (<code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvini</code> equals <code class=\"ph codeph\">udrvini</code> in the first control\n          block).</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__li_d46808e1_d46809e1_d46810e1\">The corresponding table is open\n            (<code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;uopen</code> is greater than 0).</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Connector Request Return Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__2\">Commit was successful.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__1\">-3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__2\">Exceptional error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__1\">-9</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__2\">I/O server logon error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__1\">-16</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgp1665702917460__table_d15599e1_d15600e1_d15601e1__entry__2\">DBMS reported network error.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__p_d130514e1_d130515e1_d130516e1\">If the connector request return value is less than 0,\n        an error code must be supplied in <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrverr</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__section_ykm_mjx_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812759e302\">Service Functions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Not applicable.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__section_gfx_kjx_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812759e311\">Extra information</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__p_d130526e1_d130527e1_d130528e1\">See the extra information in Commit ('C').</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__section_zlz_njx_fwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d812759e321\">TM-Controlled Connectors (Commit request)</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Connectors that are TM-controlled (<code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;TMEnabled=1</code>) do not receive\n        any Commit or Rollback requests.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgp1665702917460__p_d130532e1_d130533e1_d130534e1\">The transaction manager sends these requests directly\n        to the DBMS. Therefore, TM-controlled DBMS connectors cannot perform resource management and\n        internal administration when a transaction has ended. Also, TM-controlled DBMS connectors\n        cannot administer <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;ulock</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azl1665702915888.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uctrl</a><p>Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wfn1665702917392.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Commit ('C')</a><p>Commit the transaction on the current logon path. If the DBMS does not support Commit, return 0 to Uniface.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrb1665702976299.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>TM-Controlled DBMS Connectors</a><p>A database connector can be controlled by a transaction manager only if it is TM-capable. Uniface does not provide TM-controlled connectors and does not directly support third-party transaction managers. However, you can use the APIs provided by the Database Connector Interface to build a custom database connector that does.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533719\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533719\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Rollback ('R') Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Roll back the transaction. Description Roll back the transaction on the current logon path. If the DBMS does not support Rollback, return 0 to Uniface. Connectors that are TM-controlled ( uctrl->TMEnabled = 1) will not receive any Commit or Rollback requests. From Uniface Preconditions realized by Uniface—The connector is logged on to the DBMS. Table 1. Information Available from Uniface Data Structure->Element Description uctrl->iobuf Points to the general I/O buffer. uctrl->sqlbuf Points to the SQL buffer. uctrl->uchfw Uniface virtual address of the next control block. uctrl->uchbw Uniface virtual address of the previous control block. uctrl->udrvini Unique identification of the current logon path. uctrl->udrvnum Connector sequence number. uctrl->ulock Lock indicator. To Uniface The Rollback request is provided with a dummy control block. This control block does not describe a table and it does not have an associated connector workspace. If the connector maintains the field uctrl->ulock and the Rollback has succeeded, uctrl->ulock must be set to 0 for every control block that meets all the following criteria: It is for the DBMS driven by this connector ( uctrl->udrvnum equals udrvnum in the first control block). It belongs to the current logon path ( uctrl->udrvini equals udrvini in the first control block). The corresponding table is open ( uctrl->uopen is greater than 0). Table 2. Connector Request Return Values Value Description 0 Commit was successful. -3 Exceptional error. -9 I/O server logon error. -16 DBMS reported network error. If the connector request return value is less than 0, an error code must be supplied in uctrl->udrverr . Service Functions Not applicable. Extra information See the extra information in Commit ('C'). TM-Controlled Connectors (Commit request) Connectors that are TM-controlled ( uctrl->TMEnabled=1 ) do not receive any Commit or Rollback requests. The transaction manager sends these requests directly to the DBMS. Therefore, TM-controlled DBMS connectors cannot perform resource management and internal administration when a transaction has ended. Also, TM-controlled DBMS connectors cannot administer uctrl->ulock . Related Links uctrl Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table. Commit ('C') Commit the transaction on the current logon path. If the DBMS does not support Commit, return 0 to Uniface. TM-Controlled DBMS Connectors A database connector can be controlled by a transaction manager only if it is TM-capable. Uniface does not provide TM-controlled connectors and does not directly support third-party transaction managers. However, you can use the APIs provided by the Database Connector Interface to build a custom database connector that does. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}